# BODYiQ Stack

## Mobile
- Expo SDK 52+ / React Native / TypeScript
- Expo Router (file-based navigation)
- NativeWind v4 + design tokens
- TanStack Query (server state), Zustand (client state)
- React Hook Form + Zod (forms/intake)

## Backend (hybrid)
- **Supabase** — auth, Postgres, RLS, storage, Edge Functions
- **Later:** Shopify Storefront API, CareValidate via Edge Function proxies (keys never in app)

## Design tokens
- Black: `#0A0A0A`, White: `#FFFFFF`, Copper base: `#C37663`
- Copper light: `#D4957F`, dark: `#A85F4D`
- Surfaces: black/near-black; CTAs: copper gradient

## Core tables
`profiles`, `intake_responses`, `daily_plans`, `habit_logs`, `reminder_settings`

## Env vars
`EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL`, `EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` — secrets only in Edge Functions.

## Bundle ID
`com.bodyiq.app` (confirm with branding before App Store)
